{
  "texts": [
    "To this aim, different chunking techniques are explored when the input is in natural text and BPMN format.In the DFG case, fixed-size chunking and recursive chunking with different sizes (16,64,128,256,512) are tested.",
    "For the BPMN format also a tailored chunking is evaluated.",
    "In each case, the accuracy (see Formula 1) of the BPLLM in answering the queries is evaluated.",
    "The RQ2 also aims to evaluate the effects of prompts refinement on the answer accuracy.",
    "To this aim, for each question, two levels of refinement have been considered (not refined question, refined question)."
  ]
}